== 续作 ==
2017年1月3日，由Innerloop Studios前员工创立的游戏工作室Artplant获得了《秘密潜入》及大卫·琼斯角色的知识产权。不过《秘密潜入》的发行权仍归[[史克威尔艾尼克斯|史克威尔艾尼克斯]]所有。<ref>{{cite web|title=Former Project IGI devs buy IP back from Square Enix|work=Game Industry Biz|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2017-01-03-former-project-igi-devs-buy-ip-back-from-square-enix|date=2017-01-03|accessdate=2017-10-22|archive-date=2017-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171009174018/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2017-01-03-former-project-igi-devs-buy-ip-back-from-square-enix|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年5月29日，Artplant宣布《秘密潜入》系列续作《Project IGI: We're Going In》已经在开发，并将保持“高自由度”特色。<ref>{{cite web|title=Project IGI: We're Going In is in development|work=''[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]''|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/project-igi-were-going-in-is-in-development/|date=2017-05-29|accessdate=2017-10-22|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019222725/http://www.pcgamer.com/project-igi-were-going-in-is-in-development/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年，Toadman Interactive宣布100%收购Artplant<ref>{{cite web |title=Toadman förvärvar 100% av aktierna i norska spelstudion Artplant AS |url=https://news.cision.com/se/toadman-interactive-ab/r/toadman-forvarvar-100--av-aktierna-i-norska-spelstudion-artplant-as,c2560131 |website=Cision |accessdate=jun 28, 2018 |archive-date=2020-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414072559/https://news.cision.com/se/toadman-interactive-ab/r/toadman-forvarvar-100--av-aktierna-i-norska-spelstudion-artplant-as,c2560131 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年，Toadman Interactive宣布《秘密潜入》系列前传《秘密潜入：起源》（IGI: Origins）将于2021年发布。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bleedingcool.com/2019/11/09/toadman-interactive-announces-i-g-i-origins-coming-in-2021/ |title=Toadman Interactive Announces “I.G.I. Origins” Coming In 2021 |last= |first= |date= |website=Bleeding Cool |publisher= |access-date=18 November 2019 |quote= |archive-date=2019-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191112115114/https://www.bleedingcool.com/2019/11/09/toadman-interactive-announces-i-g-i-origins-coming-in-2021/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

